        <abstract>
            <p>ARW’s explanation of protective value of conspicuous coloration is ingenious.</p>
            <p>CD still holds to sexual selection with respect to beauty in male butterflies.</p>
            <p>Sexual selection and the races of man.</p> 
<p>Expression of emotions is another subject he plans to include in his essay [<hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Asks ARW to suggest an observer in Malay Archipelago to whom he might send queries [on expression].</p>
        </abstract>
